## Background Colors

### Page Backgrounds

**ALWAYS use these gradient patterns for page backgrounds:**

```typescript
// Light Mode - Page Background
className="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 via-indigo-50 to-purple-50"

// Dark Mode - Page Background
className="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 via-gray-800 to-gray-900"
// OR
className="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-950/20 via-indigo-950/20 to-purple-950/20"
```

**DO NOT use:**
- ❌ Solid colors for page backgrounds
- ❌ Different gradient directions
- ❌ Different color combinations
- ❌ `bg-white` or `bg-gray-100` for full page backgrounds

### Card Backgrounds

**ALWAYS use glassmorphism for cards:**

```typescript
// Light Mode - Cards
className="bg-white/80 dark:bg-gray-800/80 backdrop-blur-sm"

// Dark Mode - Cards
className="bg-gray-800/80 backdrop-blur-sm"
```

**With borders:**
```typescript
className="bg-white/80 dark:bg-gray-800/80 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-200/50 dark:border-gray-700/50"
```

